= bc(b-c) + c^2a - ca^2 + a^2b - ab^2
= bc(b-c) + a^2b - ca^2 - ab^2 + c^2a
= bc(b-c) + a^2(b-c) - a(b^2-c^2)
= bc(b-c) + a^2(b-c) - a(b+c)(b-c)
= (b-c)\{bc + a^2 - a(b+c)\}
